keyFacts: This is a Google subscriber information report for Tim Routch, obtained under EFTA (likely Electronic Funds Transfer Act or similar legal process).
The account was created on June 29, 2011, and shows login activity as recent as August 30, 2020.
The document is marked 'Google Confidential and Proprietary', indicating it was produced by Google in response to a legal request.
The account was associated with numerous Google services including Gmail, Calendar, Hangouts, and Location History.
The file reference EFTA00019640 suggests this is part of a series of documents obtained through legal process in the Epstein case.
